783
00:33:02,560 --> 00:33:03,830
Aba... sige.

784
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:05,000
Ikaw...

785
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:08,920
Sige.

786
00:33:10,030 --> 00:33:10,560
