sa pagsusulit sa imperyo.

817
00:34:40,460 --> 00:34:42,090
Tigilan mo na ang pang-aasar sa akin.

818
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:44,480
Nandito siya.

819
00:34:53,030 --> 00:34:53,770
Binibining Gu.

820
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:55,060
Batang Panginoong Chen.

821
00:34:58,060 --> 00:34:58,660
Binibining Yu.

822
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:00,670
Xuanqing.

823
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:06,060
Batang Panginoong Chen.

824
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:07,340
