825
00:35:08,260 --> 00:35:09,300
Maghintay ka lang.

826
00:35:09,510 --> 00:35:11,510
Hindi na ako makapaghintay na makasakay sa kabayo.

827
00:35:20,190 --> 00:35:20,920
Aalis na ako.

828
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:21,680
