829
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:24,320
Hyah!

830
00:35:25,510 --> 00:35:26,000
Hyah!

831
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:31,010
Maraming tao ang nagpapraktis.

832
00:35:31,140 --> 00:35:36,230
