833
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:32,320
Wenxiu

834
00:35:32,440 --> 00:35:33,300
Tara maglaro na rin tayo.

835
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:35,180
Pupunta ako sa bukid,

836
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,370
