Magpapakatanga ka sa publiko.

841
00:35:43,550 --> 00:35:44,360
Ilan!

842
00:35:45,230 --> 00:35:45,760
Gagawin ko?

843
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:46,330
Tara na,

844
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,460
