845
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:48,280
Tara na.

846
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:48,810
Tara na.

847
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:05,550
Binabalaan kita.

848
00:36:05,550 --> 00:36:07,100
Lumayo ka kay Wenxiu.

849
