851
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,710
Hindi kita bibitawan nang basta-basta.

852
00:36:10,710 --> 00:36:11,950
Huwag kang magsalita ng walang kwentang bagay.

853
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,480
Anong mapang-akit?

854
00:36:13,550 --> 00:36:14,760
