912
00:38:27,080 --> 00:38:28,460
Doon ka ba papunta?

913
00:38:34,070 --> 00:38:34,760
Gumawa ng daan!

914
00:38:41,090 --> 00:38:42,100
Dahan-dahan!

915
00:38:45,630 --> 00:38:46,690
Ano ang ginagawa mo?

916
00:39:27,830 --> 00:39:29,360
Alam kong nagmamadali ka,

917
00:39:29,510 --> 00:39:31,300
