950
00:40:46,920 --> 00:40:48,500
Ganun lang talaga ang ugali niya.

951
00:40:48,710 --> 00:40:50,510
Malamang ay naiinis siya ng kabayo,

952
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:51,960
