993
00:42:10,150 --> 00:42:12,150
Pareho silang napakahalaga.

994
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:14,150
Paano kung mahalaga sila?

995
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:15,320
Wala akong pakialam sa kanila.

996
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,000
Huwag kang pumunta.

997
00:42:16,550 --> 00:42:17,840
Hindi maganda ang pakiramdam ko.

998
00:42:18,150 --> 00:42:20,360
Sa tingin ko ay hindi ka naman masama ang katawan.

999
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:21,920
